title: Ebro In The Morning - Jam Master Jay Trial + The Joe Rogan Situation
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 2/8/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio talking about the upcoming Jam Master Jay Trial (14), Joe Rogan (39), and what's coming from J. Cole and Kendrick (51). 

Get excited for our new segment Black Facts and the also the gurus help solve your problems. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
